title: Cubariqueño Protocol Eliot Ness Natural
description: Purchase Cubariqueño Protocol Eliot Ness Natural cigars at Privada Cigar Club
cleaned_text: Additional information is the first Protocol cigar to be blended without the use of ligero tobaccos, Eliot Ness pays homage to the American Prohibition agent who is most known for his efforts to bring down Al Capone. It utilizes a Nicaraguan Habano wrapper leaf over Esteli Habano binder and Nicaraguan viso, seco, & criollo filler leaves.
